reviewText: I was disappointed with the movie,was very low budget and the trailer was the height of it. Good actors but poor script.
A really funny and fun Christmas movie, it is suitable for viewing by the entire family.  It has adventure, suspense and comedy and is a winner that will likely become a Christmas classic!
Feel good movie during the Holiday season.  It had alot of funny parts as well as soon difficult parts.  Enjoy!

I enjoy Christmas movies, especially those that I can Identify with and share with my children.  I would definitely recommend this DVD family ad friends.

It was recieved in a timely manner and in good condition.  I had no problem with viewing.
